muxi.pwps.sdk.service

Interface PWPSPaymentListener


  • public interface PWPSPaymentListener
    Interface used to notify SDK the result of payment solicitation It is notify when the payment process had some problem or it is finalized.

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      void onPaymentError(PWPSTransactionResult transactionStatus)
      The payment faced some problem and it can't be finalized It receives data transaction result with payment status informing what was the specific error that occurs.
      void onPaymentSucess(PWPSTransactionResult transactionStatus)
      The payment occurs without problems and the payment was finalized It receives data transaction result with payment receipt
